<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></span></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Thank you for getting an insurance quote from Kingsbridge.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Now you’ve reviewing your quotation documents,<b>&nbsp;is there anything you missed?</b><br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Here are the types of coverage you can add to your policy:</span></p><p class="MsoNormal"></p><ul><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Hired in Plant cover&nbsp;</b>- Covers you in the instance that plant equipment was damaged or stolen.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Own Plant cover</b>&nbsp;- Covers you in the instance that plant equipment was damaged or stolen.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Contract Works</b>&nbsp;- Covers you against accidental loss, destruction or damage for materials and labour that you've used caused by an unforeseen event in order to restore the project to its status prior to occurrence.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Professional Indemnity</b>&nbsp;- Covers you against the cost of compensating a client for loss caused by negligent services or advice</font></li></ul><p></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">If you&nbsp;<b>need to make a change to your quote</b>, reply with the best date and time for me to call you. Alternatively, you can give me a ring on<b>&nbsp;01242 808 740</b>.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Kind regards</span></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="background-color: white;">,</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><font style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</font></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>